---
// src/components/sections/AboutIdentity.astro
---

<section class="section-identity bg-white" aria-labelledby="philosophy-title">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="identity-grid">
            <div class="identity-content">
                <span class="section-badge primary">Nuestra Filosofía</span>
                <h2 id="philosophy-title">
                    No construimos islas, creamos ecosistemas
                </h2>
                <p class="lead">
                    Entendemos que la educación no necesita más software
                    complejo; necesita soluciones integradas que funcionen.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Nuestra misión es transformar instituciones mediante la <strong
                        >interoperabilidad absoluta</strong
                    >. Mientras otros ofrecen plataformas genéricas, nosotros
                    diseñamos arquitecturas que conectan tu ERP académico con el
                    aula virtual.
                </p>
            </div>
            <figure class="identity-visual" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="abstract-tech-frame animate-float">
                    <div class="tech-card-glass">
                        <div class="card-head">
                            <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body-content">
                            <strong>Conectividad Total</strong>
                            <p>ERP + LMS + CRM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="visual-glow"></div>
                </div>
            </figure>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-identity {
        padding: 8rem 0;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .identity-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 5rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .lead {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.2 !important;
        color: #0f172a;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .identity-content p {
        color: #64748b;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .identity-visual {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .abstract-tech-frame {
        width: 300px;
        height: 350px;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        position: relative;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }

    .identity-visual:hover .abstract-tech-frame {
        transform: rotate(2deg) scale(1.02);
    }

    .tech-card-glass {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20%;
        right: -20%;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid white;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .identity-visual:hover .tech-card-glass {
        transform: translateY(-10px) translateX(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .card-head {
        display: flex;
        gap: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .card-head .dot {
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        background: #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .visual-glow {
        position: absolute;
        inset: -20px;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle at center,
            rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .bg-white {
        background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1025px) {
        .identity-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .identity-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section-identity {
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        .abstract-tech-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
        }
        .tech-card-glass {
            right: 0;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -20px;
            top: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
        }
    }
</style>
